    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Templum Herculis <lb n="2"/>quot <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Vibius Fetialis <lb n="3"/>rei <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Osquens</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> promiserat <lb n="4"/>rece<supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>tis a re <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> HS VI <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Vibius Fetialis nepos <lb n="6"/>eius fecit et cum signo <lb n="7"/>Herculis <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edicavit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Basis ist in 2 Teile gebrochen, die corona ringsum abgeschlagen. Auf der Oberseite zwei Dübellöcher zur Befestigung der Statue. (B): Canto, AE 1974: Z. 3: Osquensi, Canto: Z. 4: [tot] ar(gentis) p(ondis); AE 1974: Z. 4: ar(genti) p(ondo); Canto, AE 1974: Z. 6: eius cum signo; AE 1974: Z. 8: Herculis (dedit).</p>
            </div>
